text: Volodymyr Olshanskiy (born 21 February 1976) is a Ukrainian cross-country skier. He competed in the men's 15 kilometre classical event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Ukraine Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sumy
